      "content": "but \"small steps\" don't change the fact that i've ruined everything. it's just more struggle, more shame, more looking people in the eye knowing i failed them. sometimes it just seems like the most logical way to stop the hurting is to just... not have to deal with any of it anymore. it would be so much easier for everyone if i just wasn't a problem to solve.",
